title: Refrigerator DOOR KEY
description: Refrigerator DOOR KEY PartSelect Number PS12172397 Manufacturer Part Number WR01X28053 This door key is supplied by the original manufacturer for use with refrigerators and freezers. It is a metal key that is designed to lock and unlock the door of the appliance. If the key is lost or damaged, you can easily replace it to continue securing your appliances and prevent unwanted access. To use your new key, simply locate the keyhole and insert the new key. If multiple people use the refrigerator/freezer, it is recommended to consider purchasing additional keys for your convenience.
